<div>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between mb-3">
        <h3 class="fs-6 mb-0 text-uppercase fw-bold">
            Отзывы
        </h3>
        <form action="{{ path('blackdragon:reviews') }}">
            <button class="btn shadow rounded-5 fw-medium fs-12">
                Все отзывы
            </button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="border rounded-4 ps-3 pe-4">
        {% set revQnt = 3 %}
        {% for i in 1..3 %}
            <div class="d-flex gap-3  {{ i == revQnt ? "" : "border-bottom" }} pt-3 pb-4">
                <div class="bg-review border rounded-4" style="min-width:80px; height:80px;">

                </div>
                <div>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3 mb-2">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-1 ">
                            {% set rating = 4 %}
                            {% for i in 1..5 %}
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="11" height="11"
                                     fill="{% if i > rating %} #d1d1d1 {% else %} #ffc107 {% endif %}"
                                     class="bi bi-star-fill" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                                    <path d="M3.612 15.443c-.386.198-.824-.149-.746-.592l.83-4.73L.173 6.765c-.329-.314-.158-.888.283-.95l4.898-.696L7.538.792c.197-.39.73-.39.927 0l2.184 4.327 4.898.696c.441.062.612.636.282.95l-3.522 3.356.83 4.73c.078.443-.36.79-.746.592L8 13.187l-4.389 2.256z"/>
                                </svg>
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                        <a href="#" class="fs-10 text-black">15 отзывов</a>
                    </div>
                    <h4 class="fs-12 text-uppercase fw-bold">
                        Очень длинное название шины
                    </h4>
                    <p class="m-0 fs-10 croppingText">
                        Текст отзыва Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Unde itaque tenetur
                        consequuntur quae, ab corrupti expedita qui doloremque iste nam, obcaecati explicabo ut id. Amet
                        quo velit tenetur? Tempora, iste.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</div>